  "prompt": "Does breast massaging with olive oil increase breast size?",
  "response": "There is no scientific evidence to support the claim that breast massaging with olive oil or any other oil can increase breast size. Breast size is primarily determined by genetic factors, hormonal levels, and body weight. While massage can improve circulation and may promote skin health, it does not lead to an increase in breast tissue or size.\n\nSome people may believe that massaging the breasts can stimulate growth, but this is largely anecdotal. If you have concerns about your breast size or health, it's advisable to consult with a healthcare professional for appropriate advice and information.",
